  "body_html": "<div dir=\"auto\">Hello, just wanted to let you know that I am not going to be able to make 31st. I will be out of town . I think I&#39;m gonna have to hold off on the tasting for now and we&#39;ll figure this out when I get back. </div><div dir=\"auto\">If you wouldn&#39;t mind just refunding the tasting fee, that would be good</div><div dir=\"auto\">Thank you so </div><div dir=\"auto\">Monica</div><div><br clear=\"all\"><br clear=\"all\"><div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_signature\" data-smartmail=\"gmail_signature\">null</div></div></div><div><br><div class=\"gmail_quote gmail_quote_container\"><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gmail_attr\">On Tue, May 5, 2026 at 9:08 AM Comeketo Catering Team &lt;<a href=\"mailto:comeketo@m.comeketocatering.com\">comeketo@m.comeketocatering.com</a>&gt; wrote:<br></div><blockquote class=\"gmail_quote\" style=\"margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex\"><div>I´m gonna bump you to the tasting on May 31st,</div><div><br></div><div>Hope your mom gets better soon :) </div><div><br></div><div dir=\"ltr\"><div style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><div style=\"margin:8px 0px 0px;padding:0px;overflow-x:hidden;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div><div dir=\"ltr\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><div dir=\"ltr\"><div><div><div><span><br><br><br><br>-----<br>Regards,</span></div></div><div><div><strong><span>Andre Raw</span></strong><span><br></span><em><span style=\"font-size:large\"><span>​​</span></span></em><span>Catering Event Coordinator</span></div></div><div><div><span style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><span>📲 </span></span><span>C: </span><a href=\"tel:19782353791\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\"><span>(978) 235-3791</span></a></div></div><div><div><span>📲 W: </span><a href=\"tel:9783811212\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" style=\"color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\"><span>(978) 381-1212</span></a><span><br></span