span>Sunday May 17</span></strong><span> for an incredible tasting experience. Get ready to enjoy a variety of delicious dishes, meet our team, and start bringing your event vision to life!<br></span></div><div><span>📍 </span><strong><span>Location:</span></strong><span> 199 Main St., Fitchburg, MA 01420<br>⏰ </span><strong><span>Arrival Time:</span></strong><span> 2:00 PM </span><strong><span>Please arrive 15 minutes earlier!</span></strong></div><div><br></div><div><span>Come hungry and ready to enjoy! If you have any last-minute questions, feel free to reach out. We can’t wait to see you there! 😃🔥</span></div><div><span><img src=\"cid:ii_19dfa1dd602ea654a7f1\" alt=\"image.png\" style=\"width:852px;max-width:100%\"></span></div><div><br></div><div dir=\"ltr\"><div style=\"color:rgb(34,34,34)\"><div style=\"margin:8px 0px 0px;padding:0px;overflow-x:hidden;font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span><br><br><br><br>-----<br>Regards,</span></span></div></div><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>Andre Raw</span></span></strong></div><div><br></div><div><em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>​​</span></span></em><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>Catering Event Coordinator</span></span></div></div><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>📲 C: </span></span><a href=\"tel:19782353791\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>(978) 235-3791</span></span></a></div></div><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><div style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>📲 W: </span></span><a href=\"tel:9783811212\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:rgb(17,85,204)\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif\"><span>(978) 381-1212</span></span></a></div><div><br></div><div><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/comeketocatering\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Google Sans&quot;,Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;colo